data.description: Brand New Custom Home in gated lake community. This new home features 2 living areas, the second upstairs living includes the office and has plenty of room for entertaining. The open floor plan sports modern features and design elements, decorative lighting, custom floor tile, custom tiled baths and backsplashes, spacious bedrooms, main floor master with custom en suite and a huge closet. This builder has efficiency in mind with SS Energy Star appliances, Zoned Trane HVAC, double-paned windows, highly efficient WH and much more. You'll love the oversized lot with a large backyard, sprinkler system and beautiful views. Hard to find this sized NEW home in Granbury at this price! Come see it while you still can!
